graph TD
    User([User])
    Dashboard["DashboardOverview Component"]
    UseDashboard["useDashboardData Hook"]
    DashboardService[DashboardService]
    API_Cases["API: Cases"]
    API_Invoices["API: Invoices"]
    API_Risks["API: Risks"]
    Backend["NestJS Backend"]
    DB[(PostgreSQL)]

    User -->|View Dashboard| Dashboard
    Dashboard -->|Call| UseDashboard
    UseDashboard -->|Call| DashboardService
    DashboardService -->|Promise.all| API_Cases
    DashboardService -->|Promise.all| API_Invoices
    DashboardService -->|Promise.all| API_Risks

    API_Cases -->|GET /cases/stats| Backend
    API_Invoices -->|GET /invoices| Backend
    API_Risks -->|GET /risks| Backend

    Backend -->|Query| DB
    DB -->|Results| Backend
    Backend -->|Responses| DashboardService

    DashboardService -->|Aggregate Data| UseDashboard
    UseDashboard -->|Stats Object| Dashboard
    Dashboard -->|Render Charts/Metrics| User